965
01:21:58.030 --> 01:21:59.361
<i>mengetahui tentangmu.</i>

966
01:22:01.270 --> 01:22:04.274
<i>That absurd hope has
devoured the weak base</i>


967
01:22:04.390 --> 01:22:06.991
<i>On which I had
built my new life.</i>


968
01:22:09.110 --> 01:22:10.935
<i>Sekarang aku tidak punya apa-apa.</i>

969
01:22:12.030 --> 01:22:13.880
<i>Hanya kau yang ada.</i>

970
01:22:14.990 --> 01:22:18.219
